title: Muni Long Interview and More
itunes:title: Muni Long Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had first timer Muni Long stop by where she spoke about her solo debut, embracing her star power, ex boyfriend preventing Drake collab and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day to a woman who fired a gun at a man that refused to give her oral sex, and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
